 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt'><b
style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style=3D'font-family:"Times New=
 Roman","serif"'>Мужчина-Бык</span></b><span
style=3D'font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'>: У него характер созерцате=
льный,
